summary: Both REQ-34 and REQ-35 are fully implemented. A new RightsPage.tsx has been created with 7 distinct content sections covering all required patient rights topics, using cards and callout boxes consistent with the warm teal-green design system. The page is registered as a route at '/healthcare-rights' in App.tsx, a navigation link 'Know Your Rights' is added in Navigation.tsx, and a quick-link card with Shield icon is added to the HomePage quick-links grid. No location-specific references were found. No missing requirements or hallucinated features were identified.
